    <refsection id="Description_EXPBLK_m">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
            The output of this block is a vector y with y[i]=a^u[i], where the parameter <emphasis role="bold">a</emphasis>
            is a positive scalar and u the input vector. The input and output port sizes are determined by the compiler.
        </para>
    </refsection>
